== Exercise: Define key bindings

=== Create binding context entries
		
			Select the
			_Binding Contexts_
			entry in your application model.
			Define a new entry with the
			`org.eclipse.ui.contexts.dialogAndWindow`
			ID. As name use "Windows and Dialogs".
		
		
